  "description": "Purification of semiconductor process chemicals to 9N+ (99.9999999%) purity: sub-boiling distillation in PTFE/quartz apparatus, isothermal distillation, ion exchange, and zone refining. Electronic-grade HF (<10 ppt metals), H₂O₂ (<100 ppt), HCl, HNO₃, H₂SO₄, IPA, and NH₄OH. Cleanroom packaging in PFA containers under ISO 4 conditions.",
